<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>138</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Yesu, Mulokozi wange:
 Lero nze wuwo wenka;
 Omusaigwo gunazi'za
 Yesu Mwana gwendiga.

[C1]
   Tukutendereza, Yesu,
   Yesu Mwana gwendiga;
   Omusaigwo gunazi'za;
   Nkwebaza, Mulokozi.

[V2]
 Eda nafuba bufubi
 Okufuna, emirembe;
 Lero maliride dala
 Okweyabiza Yesu.

[V3]
 Nababuliranga bantu
 Obulokozi bwona,
 Obutali bwa kitundu
 Obulamba obwobuwa

[V4]
 Nategezanga ebya Yesu
 Nobuvumunesitya;
 Eyanzijya mu busibe
 Nokuwonya eyamponya.

[V5]
 Nebaza eyanunula nze;
 Eyamponya wa kisa!
 Yesu ankuma
 Ansanyusaera,
 Bulijo yebazibwe.</lyrics>
<title>Tukutendeleza Yesu (Luganda) TZR138</title>
</song>